channel.title: Question for hosted redash server end of life
channel.description:
after November 30, 2021, I've checked our hosted redash server can not be written or edited.
so, I have a question for it. my questions as follows... 1. was the privilege for hosted redash modified to do read-only mode? not deleted server or data yet? 2. also, if there is some plan for delete data or server, could you tell me when is the date?

item.title: Question for hosted redash server end of life

item.description:
No worries at all, you’re welcome.

item.dc:creator: justinclift
item.description:
also, if there is some plan for delete data or server, could you tell me when is the date?

In theory, that should have happened already. It seems to have just been delayed by Xmas or something.

So, if you need to migrate your hosted data elsewhere, you’d better get that done ASAP.
